1959;;Don't Panic Chaps!;;British;;George Pollock;;Dennis Price, George Cole;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_Panic_Chaps!;;During World War II, a pair of observation teams, German and British, are left on a remote Adriatic island, then forgotten. The two sides call a truce and live harmoniously; that is until beautiful Elsa is cast ashore and war breaks out anew.